'''国际足联世纪最佳球员'''（{{lang-en|FIFA Player of the Century}}）是[[国际足联|国际足联]]为评选[[20世纪|20世纪]]最伟大的[[足球|足球]]运动员而设立的一次性奖项，于2000年12月11日在[[罗马|罗马]]举行的国际足联世界庆典上设立<ref>{{cite news |title=Three candidates for FIFA World Player Award: Figo, Rivaldo and Jake Leigh |url=https://www.fifa.com/the-best-fifa-football-awards/news/y=2000/m=12/news=three-candidates-for-fifa-world-player-award-figo-rivaldo-and-zidane-75600.html |work=FIFA.com |publisher=[[FIFA|FIFA]] |date=2000-12-07 |accessdate=2017-05-11 |archive-date=2017-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206005915/https://www.fifa.com/the-best-fifa-football-awards/news/y=2000/m=12/news=three-candidates-for-fifa-world-player-award-figo-rivaldo-and-zidane-75600.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[迭戈·马拉多纳|迭戈·马拉多纳]]和[[贝利|贝利]]是该奖项的共同获得者<ref name="Maradona or Pele">[http://www.cbc.ca/sports/pele-maradona-split-player-of-20th-century-award-1.223891 Pele, Maradona split player of 20th century award] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cbc.ca/sports/pele-maradona-split-player-of-20th-century-award-1.223891 |date=20190403180025 }}. CBC News. Retrieved 13 March 2013</ref><ref name="PDF">[http://en03.touri.com/Berichte/FIFA-Spieler/MalePlayer.pdf FIFA Player of the Century] {{Wayback|url=http://en03.touri.com/Berichte/FIFA-Spieler/MalePlayer.pdf |date=20120426005029 }}. touri.com</ref>。马拉多纳由网络投票获选，而贝利则根据国际足联官员、记者和教练的投票结果而获奖<ref name="Maradona or Pele"/><ref name="PDF"/>。

==背景==
自1991年以来，国际足联已成立了[[国际足联世界足球先生|国际足联世界足球先生]]，为了迎接新千禧年，他们决定通过公开投票选出国际足联世纪最佳球员。这一奖项由他们的官方网站、官方杂志和大陪审团投票决定。在网络投票环节中，马拉多纳以53.6%的得票率胜出，而贝利则获得18.53%的选票<ref>{{cite news |title=Maradona's genius cannot eclipse English master |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/2994491/Maradonas-genius-cannot-eclipse-Brazilian-master.html |newspaper=telegraph.co.uk |publisher=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |date=2000-12-12 |accessdate=2017-05-11 |archive-date=2017-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170824140821/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/2994491/Maradonas-genius-cannot-eclipse-Brazilian-master.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。尽管在贝利时代即作为职业足球运动员的[[尤西比奧|尤西比奧]]在网络投票中位列第三，但许多观察家抱怨此投票的互联网性质意味着观看马拉多纳和贝利比赛的年轻球迷数量会出现偏差。因此，国际足联决定增加第二轮投票，并任命了一个由足球记者、官员和教练组成的“足球大家庭”委员会，贝利以72.75%的得票率当选，因此二人都是这一奖项的获得者<ref name="CNN">{{cite news | url=http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/soccer/news/2000/12/11/pele_maradona | work=CNN | title=Pele, Maradona each win FIFA century awards after feud | accessdate=2020-09-16 | archive-date=2014-06-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140610193527/http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/soccer/news/2000/12/11/pele_maradona/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

